<p>John and Dave took the Main Stage last Thursday just as the show floor opened at Macworld Expo and recorded Mac Geek Gab 243 to a packed house. The two shared their thoughts on some of their show-floor picks, then went on to take questions from the audience which, to the geeks&#39; surprise, mostly seemed to center around Apple&#39;s Mail.app. Definitely a fun show, and definitely something you don&#39;t want to miss!</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
